text: Ryan Swain is an English television, radio presenter and comedian. He was born in Malton, North Yorkshire, England. He was runner-up for the Yorkshire Media Personality Of The Year Award in The Yorkshire Choice Awards. Swain formerly presented the Saturday night show on York's Minster FM. == References == Category:Living people Category:English television presenters Category:English radio presenters Category:People from Malton, North Yorkshire Category:1990 births
